---
title: Cheesy Mushroom & Zucchini Flatbreads with Creamy Chive Sauce & Lemon
description: In this veggie-topped version of a white pizza, crispy flatbreads are spread with a quick homemade creamy chive sauce and topped with golden-brown sautéed mushrooms and zucchini, fresh tomato, and a blend of easy-melting Italian cheeses. Sprinkle with fresh chopped chives and a bright squeeze of lemon juice, and dig right in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66019404da283ecbc2883bc5-0a3175f0.jpeg
